      "titleText": "Switching Users",
      "titleColor": "#00ff41",
      "titleSize": 48,
      "subtitleText": "",
      "subtitleColor": "#2a6b3a",
      "bodyText": "The - in su - loads the target user's full environment (profile, PATH, etc.). Without it you keep the calling user's environment.",
